```

B) Poll for completed jobs (@Scheduled every 5 seconds):

```sql
SELECT job_id, masterbook_id, result, status
FROM recon_job_queue
WHERE status = 'COMPLETED'
  AND processed_by_fobo = FALSE
ORDER BY completed_at ASC
LIMIT 50
FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED;
```

