```sql
UPDATE recon_job_queue
SET status = CASE
  WHEN retry_count + 1 >= max_retries THEN 'DEAD_LETTER'
  ELSE 'PENDING'
END,
retry_count = retry_count + 1,
claimed_by = NULL,
lease_expires = NULL
WHERE status = 'PROCESSING'
  AND lease_expires < NOW();
```

D) Startup recovery (reclaim this instance’s orphaned jobs on boot):

```sql
UPDATE recon_job_queue
SET status = 'PENDING', claimed_by = NULL, lease_expires = NULL
WHERE claimed_by = :thisInstanceId
  AND status IN ('SUBMITTED', 'PROCESSING');
```

